data.description: Sellers request 24 hours to show.  Incredible price reduction.  The best priced single family home w/basement apartment in the area!  Easy to add separate entry on side of home.  This is the best price/sq ft in the area!  Ask us about our bid to add a separate entrance for the apartment! Rarely will you encounter a home of such exceptional livability, thoughtful design, and meticulous finishing that offers a serene retreat from your busy life. Even more exceptional in this price range is the fully finished home, boasting over 3200 sq ft of living space.The TOP LEVEL boasts 4 GENEROUSLY SIZED BEDROOMS and a sprawling bonus/family room, providing an exclusive family entertainment area separate from the main floor. The master suite encompasses an oversized room and a beautifully appointed bathroom featuring a separate soaking tub and a glass door shower.Another remarkable feature of this extraordinary home is the fully and professionally finished basement, complete with a FULL MOTHER-IN-LAW APARTMENT featuring upgrades like a well-appointed kitchen, new appliances, a full pantry, and a separate laundry room. Such a find is exceptionally rare in this price bracket and has the potential to generate significant rental income for the fortunate new owner. (NOTE: Adding a separate walkout for complete separation of the lower level space is easily achievable.)The main floor of this capacious and well-designed home boasts an open floor plan with 9 foot ceilings, and an expansive great room seamlessly adjoining an upgraded kitchen replete with high-end appliances (included) and a a dedicated office space.Access the the oversized garage is just steps away too.   This home also features 2 furnaces, and 2 AC units for added comfort on each level of the home.  The whole home features upgraded LVP flooring, carpet and tile.  The backyard is fully fenced andis currently xeriscaped for low-maintenance living. However, it could be easily re-sodded (with sellers willing to consider contributing $2500 at closing to cover that cost). The location of this home is just as amazing as the home itself.This home is conveniently situated in the desirable Herriman area, just a two-minute walk from one of the area's top elementary schools. It's just a few minutes from freeway access and provides quick commute access to your work, no matter where it is.Close to shopping, tons of restaurants, and entertainment areas, in a growing and vibrant community makes this a no-brainer.How can it get better than this??Call Jon today to schedule a private tour.
